text: “Au gu hagau adu dagu magi huaidu gi goodou be di mee dela ne hai anga gi digau Egypt. Au gu daaligi godou dama daane i lodo tauwa ne hai, mo di kae gi daha godou hoodo. Gei Au guu haa gi lodo godou uhi di bilau dangada made i lodo godou waa hale laa, gei goodou digi huli hoou belee loomoi gi di Au.
